Third-party components
----------------------

This package bundles pre-compiled binaries of Vluzacn's ZHLT v34
(hlcsg.exe, hlbsp.exe, hlvis.exe, hlrad.exe). These tools are the work of
Vluzacn and prior authors in the ZHLT lineage (Zoner's Half-Life Tools,
derived from id Software's Quake BSP compiler). No explicit open-source
license has been published for these tools.

By using this package you acknowledge that:
- The bundled binaries are third-party software not covered by the MIT
  license above.
- You are responsible for ensuring your use of the binaries complies with
  any applicable upstream terms.
- The original ZHLT source and binaries can be found at:
  https://github.com/Vluzacn/ZHLT
